original_title: Paris and Nicole Go to Jail
overview: Paris and Nicole live very sexy lives filled with wealth, beauty, and fame, but all that couldn't save these Beverly Hills princesses' from the long arm of the law. And when they get their spoiled little asses thrown in jail, they find themselves leading completely different lives. In the end, they have a much better time than expected. They have some very sexy adventures with their new friends, and they learn how to use their own bodies as currency to survive and to get what they want. That's hot!
title: Paris and Nicole Go to Jail
